OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry start inland but
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain soon spreading in
OL,7,Ffrom the west, turning heavy at times.
OL,8,FBecoming a little brighter during the
OL,9,Fafternoon with a few sunny intervals
OL,10,Fbut further heavy showers are expected.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining mostly cloudy this
OL,13,Fevening and tonight with frequent
OL,14,Fshowers, some heavy, and a few drier
OL,15,Fclearer intervals. Mainly light winds,
OL,16,Fbut quite breezy along the Ayrshire
OL,17,FCoast.
OL,18,
OL,19,CThursday:FRather cloudy with rain or
OL,20,Fshowers, some turning heavy at times.
OL,21,FWinds will be mainly light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
